      "develop, a history of conditions like wheezing, asthma, hay fever, or eczema.\n",
      "This high prediction comes from several factors we discussed. The most\n",
      "important contributors were symptoms your child has experienced, such as\n",
      "wheezing in the past year, frequent colds, and how these have impacted their\n",
