      "\n",
      "**Environmental Contribution Confidence:**\n",
      "\n",
      "Moderate \u2014 The presence of a gas stove was a notable environmental factor\n",
      "highlighted by the model, even though current symptom history was more\n",
      "dominant.\n",
      "\n",
      "================================================================================\n"
     ]
    }
